B.MP=new A.a_(B.N6,["Discourse construal: collective-disorder circulation around {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publish ward-level incident timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 separate lawful assembly from disorder with verified arrest/charge data. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Convene community liaison with protest organisers and affected businesses on {subject}{topic_suffix} within 14 days. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Announce differentiated enforcement criteria for {subject}{topic_suffix} with a public compliance tracker. {flow_hook}","Publish granular protest incident data for {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 peaceful vs. disorder counts by ward.","Stand up independent community forums where grievance narratives on {subject} are recorded, not dismissed.","Pair enforcement updates on {subject} with named liaison officers and published response-time targets.","Review public-order messaging on {subject}{topic_suffix} for selective-condemnation bias (\u03c3).","Discourse construal: institutional framing compressing {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Issue a clause-by-clause public response to {subject}{topic_suffix}, citing evidence for each condemnation line. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Hold a press briefing allowing follow-up questions on {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 not pre-approved questions only. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Commit to a 30-day review of messaging on {subject}{topic_suffix} with an independent fact-check partner. {flow_hook}","Release timestamped evidence packets for each claim in {subject}{topic_suffix}.","Open a structured Q&A channel on {subject} for journalists and affected communities.","Audit institutional drag (I\u03c4) where {resistance_snip} slows corrective response.","Differentiate peaceful civic expression from criminal acts in all {subject} communications.","Discourse construal: macro-economic and labour-pressure circulation on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publish cost-impact tables for {subject}{topic_suffix} showing who bears disruption vs. relief. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Broker a timed negotiation on {subject}{topic_suffix} with unions, employers, and rider/user groups. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Announce phased reopening or relief steps for {subject}{topic_suffix} with measurable milestones. {flow_hook}","Publish daily disruption metrics for {subject}{topic_suffix} with cost borne by households and firms.","Convene a tri-party table on {subject} \u2014 labour, management, and service users \u2014 with published minutes.","Address stated resistance: {resistance_snip}","Preserve nuance in rider/user messaging: {flow_snip}","Discourse construal: electoral vortex polarising {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Release a voter-facing fact sheet on {subject}{topic_suffix} separating campaign claims from verified records. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Host a neutral-format public forum on {subject}{topic_suffix} with equal time for competing narratives. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publish audit-ready timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} decisions before voting windows close. {flow_hook}","Publish claim-vs-record matrices for {subject}{topic_suffix} with source links.","Fund neutral civic-information sessions on {subject} in high-shear districts.","Reduce institutional drag on electoral transparency for {subject}.","Track trust-transport (J\u03bc) gaps across voter segments on {subject}.","Discourse construal: narrative-lens compression on trust around {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Acknowledge where {subject}{topic_suffix} framing compressed nuance \u2014 publish a corrective narrative map. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Invite critics of {subject}{topic_suffix} to a structured evidence exchange, not a single podium. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Deploy differentiated outreach on {subject}{topic_suffix} for groups whose trust transport diverges. {flow_hook}","Map two-tier perception gaps on {subject}{topic_suffix} with quoted community sources.","Replace blanket condemnation lines on {subject} with event-level differentiation.","Address institutional scepticism: {resistance_snip}","Strengthen differentiated messaging: {flow_snip}","Discourse construal: accountability pressure on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Hold an open press briefing on {subject}{topic_suffix} with published decision criteria and timelines. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Commission an independent summary of institutional process around {subject}{topic_suffix}. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Set binding review dates for {subject}{topic_suffix} with public progress markers. {flow_hook}","Publish decision criteria and timelines for {subject}{topic_suffix} before speculation hardens.","Independent process review for {subject} \u2014 scope, witnesses, and publication date fixed.","Reduce procedural drag where {resistance_snip}","Maintain transparent status updates on {subject} through the review window.","Discourse construal: open-ended \u03c9 scenario on {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Convene a scenario-specific public session on {subject}{topic_suffix} anchored to the stated \u03c9 question. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Map stakeholder positions on {subject}{topic_suffix} from the supplied \u03c3/I\u03c4 inputs. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publish time-bound next steps on {subject}{topic_suffix} reflecting stated J\u03bc nuance. {flow_hook}","Ground public updates on {subject}{topic_suffix} in the user-stated \u03c9 question: {vortex_snip}","Address shear bias where stated: {shear_snip}","Work through institutional resistance: {resistance_snip}","Preserve trust-transport nuance: {flow_snip}","{agent}: Convene a public progress review on {subject}{topic_suffix} to sustain covariant continuity. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Publish constructive milestones on {subject}{topic_suffix} with community co-design. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Reinforce differentiated trust transport on {subject}{topic_suffix} across stakeholder groups. {flow_hook}","Sustain progressive momentum on {subject}{topic_suffix} with published cohesion indicators.","Co-design outreach on {subject} with groups where J\u03bc transport is strongest.","Reduce residual friction: {resistance_snip}","Amplify stated nuance: {flow_snip}"],t.w)
B.MQ=new A.a_(B.N6,["Construal del discurso: circulaci\xf3n de desorden colectivo en torno a {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publicar cronolog\xedas de incidentes por distrito para {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 separar asamblea l\xedcita del desorden con datos verificados de detenciones/cargos. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Convocar enlace comunitario con organizadores de protestas y comercios afectados sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} en 14 d\xedas. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Anunciar criterios de aplicaci\xf3n diferenciados para {subject}{topic_suffix} con un registro p\xfablico de cumplimiento. {flow_hook}","Publicar datos granulares de incidentes de protesta para {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 recuentos pac\xedficos vs. desorden por distrito.","Crear foros comunitarios independientes donde las narrativas de queja sobre {subject} se registren, no se descarten.","Emparejar actualizaciones de orden p\xfablico sobre {subject} con oficiales de enlace nombrados y plazos de respuesta publicados.","Revisar el mensaje de orden p\xfablico sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} por sesgo de condena selectiva (\u03c3).","Construal del discurso: encuadre institucional que comprime {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Emitir una respuesta p\xfablica cl\xe1usula por cl\xe1usula sobre {subject}{topic_suffix}, citando evidencia para cada l\xednea de condena. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Convocar una rueda de prensa con preguntas de seguimiento sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} \u2014 no solo preguntas preaprobadas. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Comprometerse a una revisi\xf3n de 30 d\xedas del mensaje sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con un socio independiente de verificaci\xf3n de hechos. {flow_hook}","Publicar paquetes de evidencia con marcas de tiempo para cada afirmaci\xf3n en {subject}{topic_suffix}.","Abrir un canal estructurado de preguntas y respuestas sobre {subject} para periodistas y comunidades afectadas.","Auditar el arrastre institucional (I\u03c4) donde {resistance_snip} ralentiza la respuesta correctiva.","Diferenciar expresi\xf3n c\xedvica pac\xedfica de actos delictivos en todas las comunicaciones sobre {subject}.","Construal del discurso: circulaci\xf3n de presi\xf3n macroecon\xf3mica y laboral sobre {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publicar tablas de impacto de costos para {subject}{topic_suffix} mostrando qui\xe9n asume la disrupci\xf3n frente al alivio. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Mediar una negociaci\xf3n con plazo sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con sindicatos, empleadores y grupos de usuarios. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Anunciar pasos de reapertura o alivio por fases para {subject}{topic_suffix} con hitos medibles. {flow_hook}","Publicar m\xe9tricas diarias de disrupci\xf3n para {subject}{topic_suffix} con el costo asumido por hogares y empresas.","Convocar una mesa tripartita sobre {subject} \u2014 sindicatos, gesti\xf3n y usuarios \u2014 con actas publicadas.","Abordar la resistencia indicada: {resistance_snip}","Preservar el matiz en el mensaje a usuarios: {flow_snip}","Construal del discurso: v\xf3rtice electoral que polariza {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Publicar una hoja informativa para votantes sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} separando afirmaciones de campa\xf1a de registros verificados. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Organizar un foro p\xfablico en formato neutral sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con tiempo igual para narrativas competidoras. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publicar cronolog\xedas listas para auditor\xeda sobre decisiones de {subject}{topic_suffix} antes del cierre de ventanas electorales. {flow_hook}","Publicar matrices afirmaci\xf3n-vs-registro para {subject}{topic_suffix} con enlaces a fuentes.","Financiar sesiones neutrales de informaci\xf3n c\xedvica sobre {subject} en distritos de alta cizalla.","Reducir el arrastre institucional sobre transparencia electoral para {subject}.","Seguir brechas de transporte de confianza (J\u03bc) entre segmentos de votantes sobre {subject}.","Construal del discurso: compresi\xf3n de lente narrativa sobre la confianza en {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Reconocer d\xf3nde el encuadre de {subject}{topic_suffix} comprimi\xf3 matices \u2014 publicar un mapa narrativo correctivo. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Invitar a cr\xedticos de {subject}{topic_suffix} a un intercambio estructurado de evidencia, no a un solo podio. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Desplegar alcance diferenciado sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} para grupos cuyo transporte de confianza diverge. {flow_hook}","Mapear brechas de percepci\xf3n de dos niveles sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con fuentes comunitarias citadas.","Reemplazar l\xedneas de condena general sobre {subject} con diferenciaci\xf3n a nivel de evento.","Abordar el escepticismo institucional: {resistance_snip}","Fortalecer mensajes diferenciados: {flow_snip}","Construal del discurso: presi\xf3n de rendici\xf3n de cuentas sobre {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Convocar una rueda de prensa abierta sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con criterios de decisi\xf3n y plazos publicados. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Encargar un resumen independiente del proceso institucional en torno a {subject}{topic_suffix}. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Fijar fechas de revisi\xf3n vinculantes para {subject}{topic_suffix} con marcadores de progreso p\xfablicos. {flow_hook}","Publicar criterios de decisi\xf3n y plazos para {subject}{topic_suffix} antes de que la especulaci\xf3n se consolide.","Revisi\xf3n independiente del proceso para {subject} \u2014 alcance, testigos y fecha de publicaci\xf3n fijados.","Reducir el arrastre procedimental donde {resistance_snip}","Mantener actualizaciones transparentes sobre {subject} durante la ventana de revisi\xf3n.","Construal del discurso: escenario \u03c9 abierto sobre {subject}{topic_suffix}.","{agent}: Convocar una sesi\xf3n p\xfablica espec\xedfica del escenario sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} anclada a la pregunta \u03c9 planteada. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Mapear posiciones de las partes sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} a partir de las entradas \u03c3/I\u03c4 suministradas. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Publicar pr\xf3ximos pasos con plazo sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} reflejando el matiz J\u03bc indicado. {flow_hook}","Basar actualizaciones p\xfablicas sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} en la pregunta \u03c9 indicada: {vortex_snip}","Abordar el sesgo de cizalla indicado: {shear_snip}","Trabajar la resistencia institucional: {resistance_snip}","Preservar el matiz de transporte de confianza: {flow_snip}","{agent}: Convocar una revisi\xf3n p\xfablica de progreso sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} para sostener la continuidad covariante. {shear_hook}","{agent}: Publicar hitos constructivos sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con co-dise\xf1o comunitario. {resistance_hook}","{agent}: Reforzar el transporte de confianza diferenciado sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} entre grupos de partes interesadas. {flow_hook}","Sostener el momento progresivo sobre {subject}{topic_suffix} con indicadores de cohesi\xf3n publicados.","Co-dise\xf1ar alcance sobre {subject} con grupos donde el transporte J\u03bc es m\xe1s fuerte.","Reducir fricci\xf3n residual: {resistance_snip}","Amplificar el matiz indicado: {flow_snip}"],t.w)
